BT 0 g /F2 20 Tf 186.0 720 Td (Chapter 2: The Coral City) Tj ET
q 0.5 G 1 w 72 710 m 540 710 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 680 Td (The submarine glided over a breathtaking sight: a massive coral reef!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 664 Td (It looked like an underwater city, bursting with color and life.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 648 Td ('A coral reef is the most biodiverse ecosystem in the ocean!' Marina said.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 632 Td (Fish of every color darted between the coral structures. Crabs scuttled along the bottom.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 616 Td (Sea turtles glided gracefully overhead. Eels peeked out from hiding spots.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 600 Td ('It is like a rainforest under the sea!' one of the young scientists exclaimed.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 13 Tf 72 564 Td (THE SCIENCE: CORAL REEFS) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 544 Td (Coral looks like rock or a plant, but it is actually made of tiny ANIMALS!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 528 Td (Each coral is made of thousands of tiny polyps that build limestone skeletons.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 512 Td (Coral has a symbiotic relationship with algae \(zooxanthellae\) that live inside it.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 496 Td (The algae give coral food through photosynthesis; coral gives algae shelter!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 480 Td (Coral reefs support 25% of all marine species despite covering less than 1% of the ocean floor.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 464 Td (The Great Barrier Reef \(Australia\) is so big you can see it from space!) Tj ET
q 0.92 g 67 374 478 89 re f Q
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 77 433 Td (SCIENCE FACT BOX) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 413 Td (* Coral reefs take thousands of years to grow - they are incredibly fragile.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 395 Td (* When water gets too warm, coral 'bleaches' \(turns white\) and can die.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 377 Td (* Some coral species can live for over 4,000 years!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 344 Td (TRY THIS!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 328 Td (Look up pictures of coral bleaching. Compare healthy \(colorful\) vs bleached \(white\) coral.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 308 Td (THINK ABOUT IT:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 10 Tf 82 292 Td (Why is it important to protect coral reefs even if you live far from the ocean?) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
